      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project lovers! This vehicle is the perfect canvas for someone looking to bring a car back to life and put their own touch on a classic. While it currently requires significant mechanical work and cosmetic attention, it's a fantastic opportunity to own a vehicle with great potential at a budget-friendly price. If you're looking for a rewarding weekend project, this is the one for you!",
