      "description": "Hey there! Looking for your next reliable ride? I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in great shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014perfect for someone who wants a solid, dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. It's clean, runs smoothly, and is ready to hit the road with you today. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
