    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a well-preserved example of careful ownership, offering a fantastic balance of performance and reliability. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch, both typical for a car of this age. The interior is exceptionally clean; the premium leather seats show only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and the dashboard remains free of any cracks or sun damage. All electronic components, including the infotainment system, heated seats, and navigation, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is sound, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced at recommended intervals. It recently passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection, and the brake pads and tires have plenty of life remaining. This is a solid, honest car that is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
